               <p>- Cooper. I am shopman to Mr. Stock, who is a <rs id="t17750426-83-viclabel409" type="occupation">linen draper</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17750426-83-victim691 t17750426-83-viclabel409"></join>, the window was broke had the ruffles taken out, I did not see it.</p>
