            . On the 17th of March, as one of the beadles of St. Andrews parish, and I were going down <placeName id="t17750426-83-crimeloc410">Holborn</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17750426-83-crimeloc410" type="placeName" value="Holborn"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17750426-83-crimeloc410" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17750426-83-off407 t17750426-83-crimeloc410"></join>, we saw two lads standing together just by the prosecutors shop, we suspected what they were about and stoped to watch them, they went to the window, and went away again; I sent the other person to look at the window a there was a hole in the corner, we went into a house opposite, we saw them come back, the prisoner 
               <persName id="t17750426-83-person693">
                  drew
               <interp inst="t17750426-83-person693" type="given" value="drew"></interp>
