             the ruffles out and ran away, I pursued him and took him, and found the ruffles on him.</p>
               <p>The ruffles were produced in court, and deposed to by Cooper.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence.</p>
               <p>I picked the ruffles up in Holborn.</p>
               <p>He called several witnesses who gave him a good character.</p>
